BeFit â€“ Your Personalized Fitness Companion
BeFit is an app designed to help you achieve your fitness goals through customized workout and diet plans tailored to your Body Mass Index (BMI) and delivered on a weekly basis.

Key Features
BMI-Based Customization: Get workout and diet plans specifically designed for your body type and needs.
Weekly Plans: Receive updated workout and nutrition recommendations each week to keep you progressing.
Varied Workouts: Explore a diverse range of exercise routines to prevent boredom and target different muscle groups.
Healthy Diet Plans: Discover nutritious meal plans that support your fitness journey.
